   \if#1r\endflushright\else\if#1l\endflushleft\else\endcenter\fi\fi%
}}

   \multicolumn{1}{|S{#1Banner}{p{0.7in}}|}{#1} & %
   \multicolumn{1}{|S{#1Content}{p{\notewidth}}|}{#3{\newline}}\\\hline%
   \end{tabular}%
   \end{center}%
   \ifsas@color\let\columncolor\sascolumncolor\fi%
}

}
